  <brief_title>Cingularbio® Heart Valve Clincial Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Mutli-center, Open Lable, Single Arm Study to Evaluate the Safety and Effectiveness of Cingularbio® Heart Valve in Aortic/Mitral Valve Replacement Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
